{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a fence around it, sort of a wire fence, and bushes all around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he took all these guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he put them in a blocking position.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because we could see in which direction these prisoners were running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he put them right in front of this pasture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I could see-- I was on the edge of this group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I could sort of see what-- I was looking on the side, and I could see the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "These guys were running, climbing over the fence and running into this pasture where the horses were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they were running through it, in one big group, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And as they were coming to the end, I could hear the order, fire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And you know, and they all mowed down, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was just-- it was their terrible misfortune that we happened to be working there that day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because many more could have probably escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because the forest were just not far from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I know from books that I read that only four escaped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And this was the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This was a special group that was tending the crematorium in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They blew up the crematorium when they were going to be killed themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because usually the Sonderkommando was destroyed every 90 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they knew that their time was up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they had some-- some kind of Molotov cocktails.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they had some explosive devices that they built.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And when the SS unit came in to the crematorium, they started a fight, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They threw Molotov cocktails at them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they broke through the gates, and they were running away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Unfortunately, only four escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "So we were right away assembled.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
